{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> οἰκ-ίον</b>, τό, <br /> in form <i>diminutive</i> of οἶκος, but in meaning not differing from it; in early Gr. always <i>plural</i>, <b>house, palace,</b> οἰκία ναίων [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Ilias Homerus Epicus “Illiad” 6.15, +others \">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]; <b>abode</b> of a deity, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Odyssea Homerus Epicus “Odyssey” 12.4, 8th-7th c.BC: Hesiodus Epicus “Theogonia” 744 \">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]; of the nether world, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Ilias Homerus Epicus “Illiad” 20.64 \">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]; of <b>palaces</b> containing several ranges of buildings, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Herodotus Historicus 1.35, 41, 44, 98, 3.53, 140 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; but also of <b>private houses,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] 1.59, variant in 7.118, compare 6th c.BC: Pherecydes Lerius Historicus Syr. 2, “SIG” 45.25, +others (Halic., 5th c.BC)\">Refs 6th c.BC+</a>]: so in later Prose, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.AD: Arrianus Historicus “Fragmenta Historica - FHG” 103J. \">Refs 2nd c.AD+</a>]; also of <b>nests</b> of wasps, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Ilias Homerus Epicus “Illiad” 12.168, 16.261 \">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]; of an eagle's <b>nest,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 12.221: _sing._ in later Prose, LXX.2Mac.8.33, and Poetry, 3rd c.BC: Callimachus Epicus “Fragmenta” 198, “Anthologia Graeca” 6.203 (Laco or 1st c.AD: Philippus Epigrammaticus). \">LXX+3rd c.BC+</a>]","strongNumber":"G20820","accentedUnicode":"οἰκίον","shortDef":"nest","stepGloss":"nest","stepTransliteration":"oikion","count":0,"_step_Type":"word"}]}